data.description: Location, Location, Location. Single Family Modern updated home East Boca. 2/2 home with Sub Zero Refrigerator & Freezer with one car garage with room for a pool. No HOA in the highly desirable Boca Raton Square neighborhood and in A Rated School District. Just a little over one mile to Downtown Boca with shops, dinning, beach, golf, tennis, parks and New Brightline Train Station for easy commuting. Modern, light, bright and open layout. Don't miss this amazing opportunity.
